    "bio": "I'm a developer with 5 years of experience in Python and Node.js. Over the past year, I've been building workflows to streamline operations for my team. I have also developed RAG chatbots, AI agents, and WhatsApp automation. If you need any help with N8N workflows, let's connect over a call and solve it together!",
